name: Ligar Bomba Massa
format:
<style>
  .botao {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 18px;
    color: white;
    border: 2px solid #000;
    border-radius: 5px;
    width: 200px;
    height: 80px;
    background-color: grey;
  }
</style>
  
 <button class="botao"
        ng-mousedown="send({payload: true})"
        ng-mouseup="send({payload: false})"
        ng-touchstart="send({payload: true})"
        ng-touchend="send({payload: false})">
        Bomba de Massa
</button>
